<html>
<head>
    <title>Bit Boss Battles | Launcher</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Press+Start+2P|Roboto" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link href="./stylesheets/common.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">var rev = <%= revision %>;</script>
    <script src="./javascripts/info.js"></script>
    <script src="./javascripts/cookies.js"></script>
    <script src="./javascripts/launcher.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="main">
    <div class="container" style="margin-top: 0; padding-top: 0;">
        <div style="text-align: center;"><img src="./images/logo.png"><br>
            <h1 style="font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;">By Nifty255</h1>
            <h5 style="font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;">Modified by rooLurk</h5></div>
    </div>
    <ul class="nav nav-tabs nav-justified" role="tablist">
        <li><a href="./">Home</a></li>
        <li class="active"><a>Launcher</a></li>
        <li><a href="./settings">Settings</a></li>
        <li><a href="./help">Help Page</a></li>
    </ul>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <button class="btn btn-default" id="authtwitch">Authorize BBB on Twitch</button>
            </td>
            <td>
                <p>Before you can use the widget, you must authorize it. Click the "Authorize" button to open the Auth
                    window. Once you've finished, the Auth window will close and you can then click Launch. The demo
                    will be around whether or not you authorize.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <button class="btn btn-default" id="authsl">Authorize BBB on Streamlabs</button>
                <div class="space"></div>
                <button class="btn btn-default" id="clearsl">Clear Streamlabs Authorization</button>
            </td>
            <td>
                <p>If you wish to allow donations to deal damage, you can authorize BBB to use your Streamlabs account
                    in order to look for donations. If you'd like to disable donations support, just click Clear
                    Streamlabs Authorization.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <button class="btn btn-default" id="launch" disabled>Launch Widget</button>
                <div class="space"></div>
                <button class="btn btn-default" id="demo">Launch Demo</button>
            </td>
            <td>
                <p>Click "Launch Widget" to launch the live widget in your current browser. If Bit Boss Battles won't
                    work properly in your streaming software as a web source, this is an alternate solution. If you'd
                    like to try Bit Boss Battles first, you can click "Launch Demo" to see how it works. <span
                            style="color: red;">NOTE:</span> The demo ignores all settings except sound.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <div class="container">
        <h3>Stream Source</h3>
        <p class="indent">If you use OBS or any other streaming software with browser capture, you can simply copy the
            following link to use as your source URL. (The minimum recommended size is 350px x 96px.)</p>
        <div class="link" id="link"><span
                    style="color: red;">App not yet authorized. Authorize the app to get a link.</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h3>Hard Reset</h3>
        <p class="indent">If you need to hard reset Bit Boss Battles, you can copy the link below into both this browser
            and your stream software. Once you've done so, follow the instructions on the reset page.</p>
        <div class="link" id="hdrst"><span style="color: red;">http://bbb.roolurker.xyz/reset.html</span></div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>